                Dual-Band Wi-Fi: 2.4GHz and 5GHz
                


– 

                802.11a/b/g/n
                


– 

                Bluetooth(R) Smart 4.1
                






                Customizable recording
              



– 

                Custom options to turn video and audio on and off
                






                Security & Data Protection
              



